{"tid":132141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老豆睇見個班劏房業主同金融佬就駡佢地做人唔係咁","createTime":"2017-02-23T15:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T17:41:10.000Z","uid":54581,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7eaa90112ae29b9f19745af2de48b7c9ca10971d","tid":132141,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:07:21.000Z","msg":"佢一邊屌劏房無良心，另一邊又插借錢買樓班人心態差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲叫我有錢都唔好學佢，做人最緊要按部就班，平平穩穩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係我見到佢要一邊同細佬爭書枱用，一邊同我爭電視用，一邊又要坐住張就爛都唔捨得掉既櫈<br />\n<br />\n我就忍住左道氣唔串佢了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n套劇去廣告，我無聊時望望窗外，<br />\n見到無幾遠一棟棟既公屋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n廣告後一節，我就跟佢一齊屌鳩班金融佬，地產佬，<br />\n<br />\n屌佢地無良心，吸血鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e31d1b646191f019daa1086f586d8a922c876152","tid":132141,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:09:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee80d3737cdcb0505943c59a8bd98358bb9df6f6","tid":132141,"uid":3744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:09:25.000Z","msg":"真係痴撚線 歪理當真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"552b803fd0319ad2241e23d24b02e5b0273fbe14","tid":132141,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:10:03.000Z","msg":"一個男人窮呢 就唔緊要既<br />\n<br />\n但窮得黎又要累個好老婆，又唔識教仔女，唔識給予正確思想教育呢<br />\n<br />\n就累到成家捱窮捱苦啦"},{"pid":"ba0b93e3b4c71fb16615b295df71d1eeb8b319cc","tid":132141,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>？？？有無人翻譯下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無翻譯 唔同人睇都有唔同諗法<br />\n<br />\n有共鳴既自然明"},{"pid":"b1d87e2fb882d64b0c29ef791acf048bae3c2647","tid":132141,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T15:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係痴撚線 歪理當真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/d